<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Base de données inaccessible - LSDJ</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        .gradient-bg {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }
        .lsdj-green { color: #a9df51; }
        .lsdj-bg-green { background-color: #a9df51; }
        .lsdj-dark { color: #234954; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="gradient-bg min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full text-center">
        <!-- Logo / Icon -->
        <div class="mb-12 flex justify-center">
            <div class="relative w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-50 rounded-3xl rotate-6 animate-pulse"></div>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-100/50 rounded-3xl -rotate-3"></div>
                <svg class="relative w-12 h-12 lsdj-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125" />
                </svg>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-white p-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008Z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl font-800 lsdj-dark mb-4 tracking-tight">Oups ! Connexion perdue.</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            La base de données est actuellement inaccessible.<br>
            Nos équipes techniques sont probablement déjà sur le coup.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <button onclick="window.location.reload()" class="w-full lsdj-bg-green hover:bg-[#98c948] text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-2xl transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] shadow-xl shadow-emerald-200/50">
                Réessayer la connexion
            </button>
            
            <p class="text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
                Service : LSDJ Portal
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium">
                &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Les Saveurs du Jardin. Tous droits réservés.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
